ClrHome
"Ask user for a number and square it"
Input "NUMBER? ", A
A*A->B
Disp B
Pause
ClrHome

"Loop example"
0->C
For(X, 1, 10)
  C+X->C
End
Disp "SUM=", C

"Label / Goto example"
Lbl ST
getKey->K
If K=0
Goto ST

"CE-only command (should warn)"
BackgroundOn 1

"Unmatched End (should error)"
End

"Menu example"
Menu("CHOICE", "OPT A", A, "OPT B", B)
Lbl A
Disp "PICKED A"
Stop
Lbl B
Disp "PICKED B"
Stop
